\import{table-macros}
\title{Coro concert reviewed in City News}
\author{liamoc}
\p{Our concert [Radiant Dawn](loc-0045) got a nice review in the local Canberra paper City News. You can read it [here](https://citynews.com.au/2026/choir-traces-an-emotional-path-from-sorrow-to-joy/). }
\p{Mostly the review recapitulates the programme, but I'm glad that we "sung with emotional intensity and joyful celebration."}
\p{I do agree with the one commenter though:}
\quote{
Incredibly disappointing to see the program notes were written with AI.
}
\p{I do know how this happened (things were prepared very much at the last minute), but I don't think it's an excuse. I'll have a word with Coro next time we run a concert to make sure this doesn't happen again.}